OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FOn Thursday 4 April Piran Ditta Khan
OL,7,Fwas found guilty of the murder of West
OL,8,FYorkshire Police officer Sharon
OL,9,FBeshenivsky in 2005.
OL,11,FHe was the last of seven men convicted
OL,12,Ffor their roles in an armed robbery at
OL,13,Fa travel agents in Bradford which
OL,14,Fended in tragedy.
OL,16,FITV News reporter Katie Oscroft looks
OL,17,Fback at the case and the 19-year quest
OL,18,Ffor justice.
