OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FAn unremarkable stone memorial is now
OL,7,Fthe only reminder of an incident which
OL,8,Fdominated national and international
OL,9,Fheadlines and prompted a global
OL,10,Fmanhunt lasting almost 15 years.
OL,12,FIt marks the spot outside Universal
OL,13,FExpress travel agents in Bradford
OL,14,Fwhere Sharon Beshenivsky died in 2005.
OL,16,FShe had been a police officer for just
OL,17,Fnine months when she answered a
OL,18,Froutine call towards the end of an
OL,19,Funeventful shift. A call which would
OL,20,Fultimately cost her her life.
