OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FPC Beshenivsky and her colleague,
OL,7,FTeresa Milburn, had no inkling of what
OL,8,Fwas to face them when they arrived at
OL,9,Fthe premises in Morley Street.
OL,11,FUnbeknown to them, inside, three men
OL,12,Farmed with a machine gun, a pistol and
OL,13,Fa knife were demanding thousands of
OL,14,Fpounds allegedly owed to gang
OL,15,Fringleader Piran Ditta Khan.
OL,17,FHaving discovered that the business
OL,18,Fdid not have such quantities of cash
OL,19,Fon site, the men were forced to leave
OL,20,Fwith only #5,000.
