OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FAs they did so, they were confronted
OL,7,Fby PC Beshenivsky. The 38-year-old
OL,8,Fmother-of-three had been the first out
OL,9,Fof the patrol car ` and was,
OL,10,Ffatefully, the first to cross their
OL,11,Fpath.
OL,13,FThe gang had no hesitation in using
OL,14,Ftheir weapons. PC Beshenivsky was shot
OL,15,Fat point-blank range as PC Milburn
OL,16,Fwatched in horror. PC Milburn herself
OL,17,Fwas also shot.
OL,19,FBut it was her colleague who "didn't
OL,20,Fstand a chance" PC Milburn would later
OL,21,Ftell a court.
