OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FAs she called for help ` barely able
OL,7,Fto speak ` four more members of the
OL,8,Fgang were on the lookout in the
OL,9,Fsurrounding streets, including Piran
OL,10,FDitta Khan. All seven fled.
OL,12,FThe date was 18 November ` the day PC
OL,13,FBeshenivsky's daughter Lydia turned
OL,14,Ffour.
OL,16,FAs her mother lay dying in the street,
OL,17,FLydia and her family waited for Sharon
OL,18,FBeshenivsky to come home for her party.
