OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FAmid an outpouring of anger and grief,
OL,7,Fa huge investigation was launched
OL,8,Fwhich would last almost 19 years and
OL,9,Fcross international boundaries.
OL,11,F'She just fell down'
OL,13,FHundreds of people in Bradford became
OL,14,Faware of the aftermath of the shooting
OL,15,Fas cordons were set up, roads were
OL,16,Fclosed and emergency vehicles
OL,17,Fdescended on the scene.
