OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FBut two men who worked in a repair
OL,7,Fbusiness across the road from
OL,8,FUniversal Express ` and still do to
OL,9,Fthis day ` had seen everything.
OL,11,FThey feared for their own lives after
OL,12,Fhearing gunshots and clearly seeing
OL,13,FSharon Beshenivsky collapse on to the
OL,14,Fpavement.
OL,16,FThe robbers ran past Robert Brand and
OL,17,FJohn Brambani. The pair were terrified
OL,18,Fthey would be fired on next.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/21
