OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FMr Brambani said: "The gunmen just
OL,7,Fburst out on to the street, they shot
OL,8,Fthe policewoman and she just fell down.
OL,10,F"Then they ran towards us. They were
OL,11,Fjust ten yards away, it was very
OL,12,Ffrightening, it stayed with us. We can
OL,13,Fsee the plaque from here and we
OL,14,Fremember it all the time."
OL,16,FMr Brand added: "We were down at the
OL,17,Fpolice station later that evening
OL,18,Fgiving a statement when the news came
OL,19,Fthrough that she had died. You could
OL,20,Fsee the shock, there were solemn faces
OL,21,Feverywhere, it was very sad."
