OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FThe investigation
OL,8,FTwenty-four hours after the shooting,
OL,9,Fthe police officer in charge of the
OL,10,Finvestigation, Andy Brennan, addressed
OL,11,Fa packed news conference.
OL,13,F"We will track the culprits down.
OL,14,FEvery police officer in the UK will
OL,15,Fsupport us in finding all those
OL,16,Fresponsible," he said.
OL,18,FHe could not have known at the time
OL,19,Fthat his pledge would take 19 years to
OL,20,Fcome to ultimate fruition.
