OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FBehind the scenes, the detective faced
OL,7,Fthe challenge of galvanising a team
OL,8,Fnot only investigating a murder, but
OL,9,Fgrieving the loss of one of their own.
OL,11,FHe told ITV News: "During the first
OL,12,Fbriefing with my team on the evening
OL,13,Fof Friday 19 November 2005 I said to
OL,14,Fthem, 'we will have our time to mourn
OL,15,FSharon. We won't forget her but the
OL,16,Fbest thing we can do for her now is to
OL,17,Ffind all those responsible for what
OL,18,Fhas taken place'."
OL,20,FThe pressure to solve the crime was
OL,21,Fheightened by the personal connections.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/21
