OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FRecalling his first meeting with
OL,7,FSharon Beshenivsky's husband, Paul, Mr
OL,8,FBrennan said: "It was very emotional.
OL,9,FIt was common knowledge that Sharon
OL,10,Fwanted to go early to get things ready
OL,11,Ffor (Lydia's) party.
OL,13,F"I tried to blank it out. Being a
OL,14,Ffather myself, you can imagine the
OL,15,Fgrief and the pain that Paul's going
OL,16,Fthrough and I just tried to put that
OL,17,Fto one side and to give Paul and his
OL,18,Ffamily the confidence that we would
OL,19,Fleave no stone unturned to find out
OL,20,Fwho did this to Paul's wife and the
OL,21,Fchildren's mother," he said.
