OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FThe sense that this was a very
OL,7,Fpersonal crime was reinforced as
OL,8,Funiformed officers openly wept as PC
OL,9,FBeshenivsky was laid to rest following
OL,10,Fa funeral at Bradford Cathedral on 6
OL,11,FJanuary 2006.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the investigation moved at
OL,14,Fpace.
OL,16,FOn 25 November 2005 police had named
OL,17,FSomali brothers Mustaf Jama, aged 25,
OL,18,Fand Yusaf Jama, aged 19, as well as 24-
OL,19,Fyear-old Pakistani Muzzaker Imtiaz
OL,20,FShah, as prime suspects.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/21
