OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FYusaf Jama was arrested in Birmingham
OL,7,Fthe following day. He was charged with
OL,8,Fmurder and robbery.
OL,10,FOn 12 December Shah was arrested in
OL,11,FNewport, South Wales. He was also
OL,12,Fcharged with murder.
OL,14,FA year later both were jailed for life
OL,15,Fafter being found guilty of murdering
OL,16,FPC Beshenivsky.
