OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FMustaf Jama had fled to Somalia. It
OL,7,Fwould take two years for him to be
OL,8,Fextradited to face justice and another
OL,9,Ftwo years before, in July 2009, he was
OL,10,Fjailed for life for murder.
OL,12,FBy then three other men ` brothers
OL,13,FFaisal and Hassan Razzaq and Raza Ul-
OL,14,FHaq Aslam ` were also behind bars for
OL,15,Ftheir parts in the robbery.
OL,17,FWhen Det Supt Brennan left West
OL,18,FYorkshire Police, six of the seven men
OL,19,Finvolved had been convicted of their
OL,20,Fcrimes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/21
