OL,6,FBut he would have to wait several
OL,7,Fyears before he would see the seventh
OL,8,F` the robbery's ringleader Piran Ditta
OL,9,FKhan ` face judgement.
OL,11,FThe hunt for Piran Ditta Khan
OL,13,FKnown as "uncle" by his accomplices,
OL,14,FKhan had partied with the other men
OL,15,Fthe night before the raid on Universal
OL,16,FExpress. They drank champagne and
OL,17,Fvodka and visited a brothel.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/21
