OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FWhile later claiming that the robbery
OL,7,Fwas the unintended consequence of a
OL,8,Fthrowaway comment about being owed
OL,9,F#12,000 by the business owner, in
OL,10,Freality Khan was in on the plot from
OL,11,Fthe start ` promising his fellow
OL,12,Frobbers they stood to bring back #50-
OL,13,F100,000 from their trip to Bradford.
OL,15,FHe was in the convoy of three cars
OL,16,Fwhich set off the next day from a safe
OL,17,Fhouse in Leeds to carry out the raid.
OL,19,FKhan waited in a lookout car around
OL,20,Fthe corner and ate a sandwich as the
OL,21,Fviolent events unfolded.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/21
