OL,6,FWhen the gang returned all but empty-
OL,7,Fhanded, they panicked. In the hours
OL,8,Fafter the shooting some burned their
OL,9,Fclothes and changed their appearance.
OL,10,FAll of them fled.
OL,12,FHaving spent weeks in hiding, Khan
OL,13,Fflew to Islamabad in Pakistan 16 days
OL,14,Fafter PC Beshenivsky's funeral.
OL,16,FHe would later tell police he went to
OL,17,Fattend his son's wedding and didn't
OL,18,Freturn because he knew he was under
OL,19,Fsuspicion and feared the consequences.
