OL,6,FA reward of #20,000 was offered for
OL,7,Finformation leading to his arrest.
OL,9,FIn 2014, nine years after PC
OL,10,FBeshenivsky died, police renewed their
OL,11,Fappeal for information.
OL,13,FAt the time, Det Supt Simon Atkinson `
OL,14,Fthe officer then in charge of the case
OL,15,F` renewed his force's vow that no
OL,16,Fstone would be left unturned in the
OL,17,Fquest to give PC Beshenivsky's family
OL,18,Fclosure.
