OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FAnd he made a direct appeal to the
OL,7,Fpeople of Pakistan to help bring Khan
OL,8,Fto justice.
OL,10,FBut it was another six years until, on
OL,11,F14 January 2020, Khan was finally
OL,12,Farrested and a further three years
OL,13,Fbefore he was extradited to the UK to
OL,14,Fbe charged with murder.
OL,16,FIn video footage released by West
OL,17,FYorkshire Police of Khan being booked
OL,18,Finto custody, the now grey-haired,
OL,19,Fbearded suspect could be heard saying:
OL,20,F"I never murdered anyone."
