OL,3,CPC Sharon Beshenivsky: A 19-year quest
OL,4,Cfor justice
OL,6,FHe later admitted his part in the
OL,7,Frobbery, but continued to deny
OL,8,Fresponsibility for PC Beshenivsky's
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,FBut as former detective Andy Brennan
OL,12,Fsaid: "It was solely down to him that
OL,13,Fthe travel agents was targeted and he
OL,14,Fwas also responsible for pulling that
OL,15,Fteam together.
OL,17,F"Irrespective of whether his finger
OL,18,Fwas on that trigger, Khan was
OL,19,Fresponsible for what took place that
OL,20,Fday."
