OL,6,FOn 4 April 2024, almost 19 years after
OL,7,Fhis part in the events which claimed
OL,8,Fthe life of PC Sharon Beshenivsky, and
OL,9,Fat the age of 75, Khan was forced to
OL,10,Fanswer for his crimes, his attempts to
OL,11,Fevade justice finally over.
